{
  "chapter": 19,
  "chapter_summary": "第十九回「魔眼」。武三爷闯入李大娘厅堂，以狮子吼震退两名中年妇人，用量天尺击杀一人。李大娘施展练了十年的魔眼迷惑武三爷，险些将其迷住，幸而量天尺坠地惊醒。李大娘趁机拔剑偷袭未果，被武三爷以拳风封住穴道昏倒。此时铁匠甘老头现身，以大铁锤猛攻武三爷，原来他也是血奴之一。甘老头自称血奴是十三只魔鸟也是十三个魔人，他与李大娘展开谈判，提出条件：放走一个人、毁掉一张纸，便以命相报。李大娘提及韦七娘也是血奴，甘老头笑而不语。王风在承尘上偷窥偷听，得知明珠流转之谜，担忧血奴的安全。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_nian_fu_ren_yi",
      "speaker_name": "中年妇人",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "你是少林弟子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_zhong_nian_fu_ren_yi",
      "text": "你也认得这种量天尺？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_nian_fu_ren_yi",
      "speaker_name": "中年妇人",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "那不过是块磁铁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_zhong_nian_fu_ren_yi",
      "text": "在你虽然已不是秘密，但出其不意，你还是不免上当。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "有人说你是一个女魔，男人见了你，没有一个能够不着魔，我本不信，现在却非信不可。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "连我这种少林寺出身的高手，一个不提防都几乎被你迷住，差一点的人如何能抗拒得了？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "你这双魔眼练了多少时日？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "不多不少，十年！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "你是不是仍想再试试那双魔眼能否再将我迷惑？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "甘老头！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "想不到你也是身怀绝技！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "很多事你都想不到。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "李大娘与你，是什么关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "与你有关系的只是一件事。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "你在外面的手下已一个不剩，不必再大声呼叫。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "门外的几个呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "门外的也是。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "都是你杀的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "对付他们就我一个人已经足够。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "凭你一个人就能够将他们杀光？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "你相信也好，不相信也好，我都不在乎。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "我跟你说话，其实也是多余。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "要说话我应该找一个活人。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "我还是一个活人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "在我的眼中，你已是一个死人。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "在我的眼中你也是的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "你也有杀我的把握？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "十二分把握。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "这非要见识一下不可。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "无论如何你都是非见识一下不可的了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "两虎相斗，势不俱生，死的无须说，活的也不会太好受，这种事能够避免最好。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "血鹦鹉的宝藏我只要一半已够满足。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "你的意思是与我合作？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "凭你我的武功，李大娘方面即使还有高手，应该亦可以应付得来，何况她本人现在已落在我们手中。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "你虽然已是老大的一把年纪，但身子这么强壮，势必还有相当的日子好活。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "一个人只要有钱，就算年纪大一点，也不要紧，一样可以好好的享受享受。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "你这一生大概还没有认真享受一下。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "的确还没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "那你就更不要错过这个机会了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "即使你完全没有经验也不要紧，这方面我可以说经验丰富，大可以替你好好安排一下，保管你满意。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "一个人有钱，难道不懂得怎样去享受。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "这句话有道理。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "钱据讲是没有人嫌多的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "据我所知嫌钱多的人一个也都没有。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "那我为什么要分一份给你？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "想不到你的胃口比我还大。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "我早说过，很多事你都想不到。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "我本来是什么身份你就已经想不到的了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "你本来是什么身份？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "奴才！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "奴才？谁是奴才？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "血鹦鹉！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "你也是血奴？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "正是血奴！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "血奴据讲是种鸟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "是鸟也是人！十三只魔鸟，十三个魔人。",
      "tone": "诡异",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "是哪十三个？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "你这个人的好奇心倒不轻。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "只可惜，你问的并不是时候。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "哦",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "我现在已不想说话。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "那你想怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "想见识你那必杀我的本领。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "对于我方才的提议，你真的完全不加考虑？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "对于觊觎那些珠宝的人，我向来只知道一件事。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "非杀不可。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "你就只懂得这些伎俩？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "text": "倒要看你还接得下我多少锤！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 487,
      "line_end": 487
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_san_ye",
      "speaker_name": "武三爷",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "一只手换一条命，这种生意不怕做。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 535,
      "line_end": 535
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "我实在想不到你会为我拼命。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 685,
      "line_end": 687
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "看来你伤的并不轻。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 691,
      "line_end": 691
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "你既然预备为我拼命，为什么只是等在门外，一直等到我的人伤亡殆尽才肯现身？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 695,
      "line_end": 697
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "这样你才能明白一件事情。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 701,
      "line_end": 703
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "什么事情？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 707,
      "line_end": 707
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "你的人除了那条老蛔虫之外，其他的根本不堪一击。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 709,
      "line_end": 709
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "要我明白这件事情并不是只有这种办法。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 711,
      "line_end": 711
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "这种办法却是最好的一种办法。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 713,
      "line_end": 713
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "因为这一来你就可以省回一番气力？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 715,
      "line_end": 715
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "我根本没有打算将气力用在你的人身上。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 717,
      "line_end": 717
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 719,
      "line_end": 719
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "姓武的不杀他们，我也不会杀他们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 721,
      "line_end": 721
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "你还不敢开罪我？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 723,
      "line_end": 723
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "还不敢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 725,
      "line_end": 725
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "如果敢，相信你早已杀掉他们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 727,
      "line_end": 727
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 729,
      "line_end": 729
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "所以别人杀他们，你当然不会阻止。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 731,
      "line_end": 731
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "当然。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 733,
      "line_end": 733
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "我的人死光了对你到底有什么好处？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 735,
      "line_end": 735
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "或者那我就可以不再做铁匠了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 737,
      "line_end": 737
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "不做铁匠，你打算去做什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 739,
      "line_end": 739
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "做你的手下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 741,
      "line_end": 741
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 743,
      "line_end": 743
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "你那些手下既然死光，当然需要招聘一批新的手下来保护你的安全。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 745,
      "line_end": 747
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "的确有这种需要。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 749,
      "line_end": 749
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "你的人死光，武三爷的人也是伤亡殆尽，这附近可以用的人早已被你们网罗，也即是都已尽死在这一役之中，纵使你重金招聘，亦招聘不到的了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 751,
      "line_end": 753
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "走远些也许可以解决这个问题，但目前，你却必需有个人保护左右。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 753,
      "line_end": 755
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "我走来这里，本来就是因为逃避官府的追缉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 765,
      "line_end": 765
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "除了官府，现在你还要应付另外一种人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 767,
      "line_end": 767
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "哪种人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 769,
      "line_end": 769
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "盗贼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 771,
      "line_end": 771
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "什么盗贼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 773,
      "line_end": 773
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "谭门三霸天之类。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 775,
      "line_end": 775
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "他们只是碰巧路过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 777,
      "line_end": 777
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "我看就不是了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 779,
      "line_end": 779
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 781,
      "line_end": 781
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "谭老大的身上有一颗明珠，这件事你难道不知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 783,
      "line_end": 783
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "明珠已在我手中。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 785,
      "line_end": 785
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "既然是这样，你还说谭门三霸天只是碰巧路过。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 831,
      "line_end": 833
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "就这颗明珠，亦不能证明他们的目的地是这里。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 835,
      "line_end": 835
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "武三爷凭那个送子观音的玉像找到这里，他们为什么不能凭那颗明珠找到这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 837,
      "line_end": 839
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "送子观音与明珠都不会说话，你可知他们其实是凭什么找到来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 843,
      "line_end": 845
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "你知道是凭什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 847,
      "line_end": 847
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "我也不知道，我只知道他们能够找到来，其他人也能够找到，外流的珠宝，并非只是一个送子观音，一颗明珠，那些珠宝可能落在比武三爷、谭门三霸天更厉害，更精明的人手上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 849,
      "line_end": 851
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "所以你必须及早离开这个地方。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 855,
      "line_end": 855
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "我也是这个意思。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 857,
      "line_end": 857
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "说不定他们之中已有人找到你，只不过慑于你与武三爷的势力，潜伏在附近，等机会采取行动。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 859,
      "line_end": 861
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "这是说，我一定要在高手的保护之下，才能够离开这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 863,
      "line_end": 865
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "我正是理想的人选。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 867,
      "line_end": 867
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "有一件事相信你还没有忘记。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 869,
      "line_end": 869
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "我并不是现在才知道你是一个高手，那最少已是七八年之前的事情。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 873,
      "line_end": 875
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "当时我就已重金礼聘你做保镖，而且并不止一次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 879,
      "line_end": 879
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "可是每一次你都拒绝，七八年之后的今夜，你竟然自动提出要做我的手下，我实在奇怪。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 883,
      "line_end": 885
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "一点都不奇怪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 887,
      "line_end": 887
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "这之前除了老蛔虫，你手下最少还有十三把刀，四柄剑，在你的眼中，我其实并没有多大的价值，现在可就不同了，你已经完全孤立，而我的价值自然相应增大。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 891,
      "line_end": 893
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "那又怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 895,
      "line_end": 895
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "我就可以跟你谈谈条件。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 897,
      "line_end": 897
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "你要我给你多少钱？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 899,
      "line_end": 899
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "一分钱我都不要，我准备向你提出的条件与钱根本就没有关系。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 901,
      "line_end": 903
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "那是什么条件？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 905,
      "line_end": 905
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "只要你放走一个人，毁掉一张纸，我这条命完全交给你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 907,
      "line_end": 909
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "你认为自己那条命那么有价值？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 915,
      "line_end": 917
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "以前没有，现在有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 919,
      "line_end": 919
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "因为现在我已经完全孤立，一定要你保护才能逃出这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 921,
      "line_end": 923
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "难道这不是事实。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 925,
      "line_end": 925
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "你显然忘记了一个人。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 927,
      "line_end": 927
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 929,
      "line_end": 929
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "韦七娘！我并未完全孤立，还有一个韦七娘可用。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 931,
      "line_end": 933
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "凭她的神针绝技，保护我离开这地方相信还不成问题。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 937,
      "line_end": 939
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "你在笑什么？莫非你认为韦七娘也是不堪一击？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 943,
      "line_end": 945
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "甘老头",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "她不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 947,
      "line_end": 947
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_gan_lao_tou",
      "text": "如果是，她根本也没有资格做血奴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 949,
      "line_end": 949
    }
